{
  "video_id": "pvBlSFVmoaw",
  "title": "Electrical experiments with plants that count and communicate | Greg Gage",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12580.0,
      "end_time": 13836.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a neuroscientist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 13860.0,
      "end_time": 16155.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m the co-founder of Backyard Brains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16180.0,
      "end_time": 20360.0,
      "text": "and our mission is to train the next generation of neuroscientists"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20600.0,
      "end_time": 23760.0,
      "text": "by taking graduate-level neuroscience research equipment"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23100.0,
      "end_time": 26540.0,
      "text": "and making it available for kids in middle schools and high schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27340.0,
      "end_time": 29196.0,
      "text": "And so when we go into the classroom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29220.0,
      "end_time": 33116.0,
      "text": "one way to get them thinking about the brain, which is very complex,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33140.0,
      "end_time": 36760.0,
      "text": "is to ask them a very simple question about neuroscience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36100.0,
      "end_time": 38140.0,
      "text": "and that is, \"What has a brain?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38860.0,
      "end_time": 40116.0,
      "text": "When we ask that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40140.0,
      "end_time": 44195.0,
      "text": "students will instantly tell you that their cat or dog has a brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44220.0,
      "end_time": 48796.0,
      "text": "and most will say that a mouse or even a small insect has a brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48820.0,
      "end_time": 51636.0,
      "text": "but almost nobody says that a plant or a tree"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51660.0,
      "end_time": 53836.0,
      "text": "or a shrub has a brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53860.0,
      "end_time": 56356.0,
      "text": "And so when you push --"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56380.0,
      "end_time": 58956.0,
      "text": "because this could actually help describe a little bit"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58980.0,
      "end_time": 61156.0,
      "text": "how the brain actually functions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61180.0,
      "end_time": 62396.0,
      "text": "so you push and say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62420.0,
      "end_time": 65956.0,
      "text": "\"Well, what is it that makes living things have brains versus not?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65980.0,
      "end_time": 68436.0,
      "text": "And often they&#39;ll come back with the classification"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68460.0,
      "end_time": 72235.0,
      "text": "that things that move tend to have brains."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72260.0,
      "end_time": 73876.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s absolutely correct."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 73900.0,
      "end_time": 76356.0,
      "text": "Our nervous system evolved because it is electrical."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76380.0,
      "end_time": 79515.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s fast, so we can quickly respond to stimuli in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 79540.0,
      "end_time": 81756.0,
      "text": "and move if we need to."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 81780.0,
      "end_time": 83996.0,
      "text": "But you can go back and push back on a student,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 84200.0,
      "end_time": 87760.0,
      "text": "and say, \"Well, you know, you say that plants don&#39;t have brains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 87100.0,
      "end_time": 88556.0,
      "text": "but plants do move.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 88580.0,
      "end_time": 90436.0,
      "text": "Anyone who has grown a plant"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 90460.0,
      "end_time": 92436.0,
      "text": "has noticed that the plant will move"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 92460.0,
      "end_time": 94276.0,
      "text": "and face the sun."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 94300.0,
      "end_time": 96436.0,
      "text": "But they&#39;ll say, \"But that&#39;s a slow movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 96460.0,
      "end_time": 99476.0,
      "text": "You know, that doesn&#39;t count. That could be a chemical process.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 99500.0,
      "end_time": 101876.0,
      "text": "But what about fast-moving plants?"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 101900.0,
      "end_time": 106996.0,
      "text": "Now, in 1760, Arthur Dobbs, the Royal Governor of North Carolina,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 107200.0,
      "end_time": 109556.0,
      "text": "made a pretty fascinating discovery."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 109580.0,
      "end_time": 112436.0,
      "text": "In the swamps behind his house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 112460.0,
      "end_time": 116116.0,
      "text": "he found a plant that would spring shut"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 116140.0,
      "end_time": 118820.0,
      "text": "every time a bug would fall in between it."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 119540.0,
      "end_time": 122476.0,
      "text": "He called this plant the flytrap,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 122500.0,
      "end_time": 125436.0,
      "text": "and within a decade, it made its way over to Europe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 125460.0,
      "end_time": 128995.0,
      "text": "where eventually the great Charles Darwin got to study this plant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 129199.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131360.0,
      "text": "and this plant absolutely blew him away."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 131600.0,
      "end_time": 133596.0,
      "text": "He called it the most wonderful plant in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 133620.0,
      "end_time": 135876.0,
      "text": "This is a plant that was an evolutionary wonder."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 135900.0,
      "end_time": 137876.0,
      "text": "This is a plant that moves quickly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 137900.0,
      "end_time": 139196.0,
      "text": "which is rare,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 139220.0,
      "end_time": 141196.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s carnivorous, which is also rare."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 141220.0,
      "end_time": 142676.0,
      "text": "And this is in the same plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 142700.0,
      "end_time": 144155.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;m here today to tell you"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 144180.0,
      "end_time": 146596.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s not even the coolest thing about this plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 146620.0,
      "end_time": 149140.0,
      "text": "The coolest thing is that the plant can count."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 150380.0,
      "end_time": 151756.0,
      "text": "So in order to show that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 151780.0,
      "end_time": 153956.0,
      "text": "we have to get some vocabulary out of the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 153980.0,
      "end_time": 157236.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m going to do what we do in the classroom with students."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 157260.0,
      "end_time": 161116.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to do an experiment on electrophysiology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 161140.0,
      "end_time": 164275.0,
      "text": "which is the recording of the body&#39;s electrical signal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 164300.0,
      "end_time": 166596.0,
      "text": "either coming from neurons or from muscles."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 166620.0,
      "end_time": 168956.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m putting some electrodes here on my wrists."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 168980.0,
      "end_time": 170316.0,
      "text": "As I hook them up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 170340.0,
      "end_time": 172516.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to be able to see a signal"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 172540.0,
      "end_time": 173995.0,
      "text": "on the screen here."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 174200.0,
      "end_time": 175916.0,
      "text": "And this signal may be familiar to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 175940.0,
      "end_time": 178116.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called the EKG, or the electrocardiogram."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 178140.0,
      "end_time": 180595.0,
      "text": "And this is coming from neurons in my heart"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 180620.0,
      "end_time": 183156.0,
      "text": "that are firing what&#39;s called action potentials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 183180.0,
      "end_time": 187360.0,
      "text": "potential meaning voltage and action meaning it moves quickly up and down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 187600.0,
      "end_time": 188516.0,
      "text": "which causes my heart to fire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 188540.0,
      "end_time": 191356.0,
      "text": "which then causes the signal that you see here."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 191380.0,
      "end_time": 195116.0,
      "text": "And so I want you to remember the shape of what we&#39;ll be looking at right here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 195140.0,
      "end_time": 196995.0,
      "text": "because this is going to be important."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 197200.0,
      "end_time": 199436.0,
      "text": "This is a way that the brain encodes information"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 199460.0,
      "end_time": 201156.0,
      "text": "in the form of an action potential."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 201180.0,
      "end_time": 203500.0,
      "text": "So now let&#39;s turn to some plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 204740.0,
      "end_time": 208276.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m going to first introduce you to the mimosa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 208300.0,
      "end_time": 211516.0,
      "text": "not the drink, but the Mimosa pudica,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 211540.0,
      "end_time": 214876.0,
      "text": "and this is a plant that&#39;s found in Central America and South America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 214900.0,
      "end_time": 216876.0,
      "text": "and it has behaviors."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 216900.0,
      "end_time": 218996.0,
      "text": "And the first behavior I&#39;m going to show you"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 219200.0,
      "end_time": 221116.0,
      "text": "is if I touch the leaves here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 221140.0,
      "end_time": 223339.0,
      "text": "you get to see that the leaves tend to curl up."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 225100.0,
      "end_time": 227356.0,
      "text": "And then the second behavior is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 227380.0,
      "end_time": 229555.0,
      "text": "if I tap the leaf,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 229580.0,
      "end_time": 231396.0,
      "text": "the entire branch seems to fall down."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 231420.0,
      "end_time": 232956.0,
      "text": "So why does it do that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 232980.0,
      "end_time": 234596.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not really known to science."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 234620.0,
      "end_time": 237836.0,
      "text": "One of the reasons why could be that it scares away insects"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 237860.0,
      "end_time": 240360.0,
      "text": "or it looks less appealing to herbivores."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 240600.0,
      "end_time": 242556.0,
      "text": "But how does it do that? Now, that&#39;s interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 242580.0,
      "end_time": 244716.0,
      "text": "We can do an experiment to find out."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 244740.0,
      "end_time": 246196.0,
      "text": "So what we&#39;re going to do now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 246220.0,
      "end_time": 249636.0,
      "text": "just like I recorded the electrical potential from my body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 249660.0,
      "end_time": 253476.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to record the electrical potential from this plant, this mimosa."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 253500.0,
      "end_time": 258995.0,
      "text": "And so what we&#39;re going to do is I&#39;ve got a wire wrapped around the stem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 259190.0,
      "end_time": 261990.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ve got the ground electrode where?"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 262180.0,
      "end_time": 265116.0,
      "text": "In the ground. It&#39;s an electrical engineering joke. Alright."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 265140.0,
      "end_time": 266476.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 266500.0,
      "end_time": 269236.0,
      "text": "Alright. So I&#39;m going to go ahead and tap the leaf here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 269260.0,
      "end_time": 271635.0,
      "text": "and I want you to look at the electrical recording"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 271659.0,
      "end_time": 273620.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re going to see inside the plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 274340.0,
      "end_time": 277236.0,
      "text": "Whoa. It is so big, I&#39;ve got to scale it down."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 278676.0,
      "text": "Alright. So what is that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 278700.0,
      "end_time": 281676.0,
      "text": "That is an action potential that is happening inside the plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 281700.0,
      "end_time": 282955.0,
      "text": "Why was it happening?"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 282980.0,
      "end_time": 284596.0,
      "text": "Because it wanted to move. Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 284620.0,
      "end_time": 287636.0,
      "text": "And so when I hit the touch receptors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 287660.0,
      "end_time": 290836.0,
      "text": "it sent a voltage all the way down to the end of the stem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 290860.0,
      "end_time": 292116.0,
      "text": "which caused it to move."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 292140.0,
      "end_time": 294395.0,
      "text": "And now, in our arms, we would move our muscles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 294420.0,
      "end_time": 296116.0,
      "text": "but the plant doesn&#39;t have muscles."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 296140.0,
      "end_time": 298395.0,
      "text": "What it has is water inside the cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 298420.0,
      "end_time": 301356.0,
      "text": "and when the voltage hits it, it opens up, releases the water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 301380.0,
      "end_time": 303814.0,
      "text": "changes the shape of the cells, and the leaf falls."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 304300.0,
      "end_time": 309236.0,
      "text": "OK. So here we see an action potential encoding information to move. Alright?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 309260.0,
      "end_time": 310756.0,
      "text": "But can it do more?"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 310780.0,
      "end_time": 312350.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s go to find out."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 312600.0,
      "end_time": 315116.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to go to our good friend, the Venus flytrap here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 315140.0,
      "end_time": 319556.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re going to take a look at what happens inside the leaf"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 319580.0,
      "end_time": 321515.0,
      "text": "when a fly lands on here."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 321540.0,
      "end_time": 324236.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m going to pretend to be a fly right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 324260.0,
      "end_time": 325916.0,
      "text": "And now here&#39;s my Venus flytrap,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 325940.0,
      "end_time": 327956.0,
      "text": "and inside the leaf, you&#39;re going to notice"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 327980.0,
      "end_time": 331196.0,
      "text": "that there are three little hairs here, and those are trigger hairs."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 331220.0,
      "end_time": 332596.0,
      "text": "And so when a fly lands --"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 332620.0,
      "end_time": 335116.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to touch one of the hairs right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 335140.0,
      "end_time": 336580.0,
      "text": "Ready? One, two, three."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 338820.0,
      "end_time": 341276.0,
      "text": "What do we get? We get a beautiful action potential."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 341300.0,
      "end_time": 343820.0,
      "text": "However, the flytrap doesn&#39;t close."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 344460.0,
      "end_time": 345916.0,
      "text": "And to understand why that is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 345940.0,
      "end_time": 349156.0,
      "text": "we need to know a little bit more about the behavior of the flytrap."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 349180.0,
      "end_time": 352476.0,
      "text": "Number one is that it takes a long time to open the traps back up --"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 352500.0,
      "end_time": 356676.0,
      "text": "you know, about 24 to 48 hours if there&#39;s no fly inside of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 356700.0,
      "end_time": 358396.0,
      "text": "And so it takes a lot of energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 358420.0,
      "end_time": 361636.0,
      "text": "And two, it doesn&#39;t need to eat that many flies throughout the year."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 361660.0,
      "end_time": 364316.0,
      "text": "Only a handful. It gets most of its energy from the sun."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 364340.0,
      "end_time": 367556.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just trying to replace some nutrients in the ground with flies."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 367580.0,
      "end_time": 368835.0,
      "text": "And the third thing is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 368860.0,
      "end_time": 371836.0,
      "text": "it only opens then closes the traps a handful of times"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 371860.0,
      "end_time": 373500.0,
      "text": "until that trap dies."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 373940.0,
      "end_time": 376636.0,
      "text": "So therefore, it wants to make really darn sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 376660.0,
      "end_time": 381760.0,
      "text": "that there&#39;s a meal inside of it before the flytrap snaps shut."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 381100.0,
      "end_time": 382300.0,
      "text": "So how does it do that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 383100.0,
      "end_time": 385716.0,
      "text": "It counts the number of seconds"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 385740.0,
      "end_time": 388956.0,
      "text": "between successive touching of those hairs."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 388980.0,
      "end_time": 391396.0,
      "text": "And so the idea is that there&#39;s a high probability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 391420.0,
      "end_time": 394876.0,
      "text": "if there&#39;s a fly inside of there, that it&#39;s going to be clicked together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 394900.0,
      "end_time": 397116.0,
      "text": "and so when it gets the first action potential,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 397140.0,
      "end_time": 398556.0,
      "text": "it starts counting, one, two,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 398580.0,
      "end_time": 400796.0,
      "text": "and if it gets to 20 and it doesn&#39;t fire again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 400820.0,
      "end_time": 402236.0,
      "text": "then it&#39;s not going to close,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 402260.0,
      "end_time": 405116.0,
      "text": "but if it does it within there, then the flytrap will close."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 405140.0,
      "end_time": 406596.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re going to go back now."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 406620.0,
      "end_time": 408636.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to touch the Venus flytrap again."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 408660.0,
      "end_time": 410676.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been talking for more than 20 seconds."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 410700.0,
      "end_time": 413659.0,
      "text": "So we can see what happens when I touch the hair a second time."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 415540.0,
      "end_time": 417996.0,
      "text": "So what do we get? We get a second action potential,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 418200.0,
      "end_time": 419916.0,
      "text": "but again, the leaf doesn&#39;t close."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 419940.0,
      "end_time": 421876.0,
      "text": "So now if I go back in there"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 421900.0,
      "end_time": 423796.0,
      "text": "and if I&#39;m a fly moving around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 423820.0,
      "end_time": 425996.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to be touching the leaf a few times."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 426200.0,
      "end_time": 428436.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to go and brush it a few times."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 428460.0,
      "end_time": 429876.0,
      "text": "And immediately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 429900.0,
      "end_time": 431635.0,
      "text": "the flytrap closes."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 431660.0,
      "end_time": 435796.0,
      "text": "So here we are seeing the flytrap actually doing a computation."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 435820.0,
      "end_time": 438316.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s determining if there&#39;s a fly inside the trap,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 438340.0,
      "end_time": 439835.0,
      "text": "and then it closes."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 439860.0,
      "end_time": 442260.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s go back to our original question."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 443340.0,
      "end_time": 445635.0,
      "text": "Do plants have brains?"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 445660.0,
      "end_time": 447236.0,
      "text": "Well, the answer is no."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 447260.0,
      "end_time": 448635.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no brains in here."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 448660.0,
      "end_time": 452236.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no axons, no neurons."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 452260.0,
      "end_time": 453635.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t get depressed."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 453660.0,
      "end_time": 456360.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t want to know what the Tigers&#39; score is."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 456600.0,
      "end_time": 458156.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t have self-actualization problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 458180.0,
      "end_time": 461596.0,
      "text": "But what it does have is something that&#39;s very similar to us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 461620.0,
      "end_time": 464676.0,
      "text": "which is the ability to communicate using electricity."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 464700.0,
      "end_time": 466955.0,
      "text": "It just uses slightly different ions than we do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 466980.0,
      "end_time": 468996.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s actually doing the same thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 469200.0,
      "end_time": 471195.0,
      "text": "So just to show you"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 471220.0,
      "end_time": 474516.0,
      "text": "the ubiquitous nature of these action potentials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 474540.0,
      "end_time": 476756.0,
      "text": "we saw it in the Venus flytrap,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 476780.0,
      "end_time": 478916.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve seen an action potential in the mimosa."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 478940.0,
      "end_time": 481316.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve even seen an action potential in a human."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 481340.0,
      "end_time": 484556.0,
      "text": "Now, this is the euro of the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 484580.0,
      "end_time": 486716.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the way that all information is passed."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 486740.0,
      "end_time": 489556.0,
      "text": "And so what we can do is we can use those action potentials"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 489580.0,
      "end_time": 491750.0,
      "text": "to pass information"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 491100.0,
      "end_time": 492836.0,
      "text": "between species of plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 492860.0,
      "end_time": 497276.0,
      "text": "And so this is our interspecies plant-to-plant communicator,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 497300.0,
      "end_time": 500476.0,
      "text": "and what we&#39;ve done is we&#39;ve created a brand new experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 500500.0,
      "end_time": 504360.0,
      "text": "where we&#39;re going to record the action potential from a Venus flytrap,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 504600.0,
      "end_time": 506836.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re going to send it into the sensitive mimosa."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 506860.0,
      "end_time": 508596.0,
      "text": "So I want you to recall what happens"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 508620.0,
      "end_time": 510556.0,
      "text": "when we touch the leaves of the mimosa."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 510580.0,
      "end_time": 513236.0,
      "text": "It has touch receptors that are sending that information"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 513260.0,
      "end_time": 515356.0,
      "text": "back down in the form of an action potential."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 515380.0,
      "end_time": 516716.0,
      "text": "And so what would happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 516740.0,
      "end_time": 520356.0,
      "text": "if we took the action potential from the Venus flytrap"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 520380.0,
      "end_time": 523460.0,
      "text": "and sent it into all the stems of the mimosa?"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 524260.0,
      "end_time": 527276.0,
      "text": "We should be able to create the behavior of the mimosas"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 527300.0,
      "end_time": 529195.0,
      "text": "without actually touching it ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 529220.0,
      "end_time": 531236.0,
      "text": "And so if you&#39;ll allow me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 531260.0,
      "end_time": 534715.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to go ahead and trigger this mimosa right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 534739.0,
      "end_time": 538556.0,
      "text": "by touching on the hairs of the Venus flytrap."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 538580.0,
      "end_time": 542180.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re going to send information about touch from one plant to another."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 546460.0,
      "end_time": 548156.0,
      "text": "So there you see it."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 548180.0,
      "end_time": 549396.0,
      "text": "So --"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 549420.0,
      "end_time": 555435.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 555460.0,
      "end_time": 558516.0,
      "text": "So I hope you learned a little bit, something about plants today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 558540.0,
      "end_time": 559756.0,
      "text": "and not only that."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 559780.0,
      "end_time": 562795.0,
      "text": "You learned that plants could be used to help teach neuroscience"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 562820.0,
      "end_time": 564556.0,
      "text": "and bring along the neurorevolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 564580.0,
      "end_time": 565796.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 565820.0,
      "end_time": 568540.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}